text: The 1973–1974 Algerian Championnat National was the 11th season of the Algerian Championnat National since its establishment in 1962. A total of 16 teams contested the league, with JS Kawkabi as the defending champions. ==Team summaries== === Promotion and relegation === Teams promoted from Algerian Division 2 1973–1974 * USM Alger * USM Khenchela * MC Saïda Teams relegated to Algerian Division 2 1974–1975 * JSM Tiaret * ASM Oran * WA Tlemcen ==League table== ==References== ==External links== *1973–74 Algerian Championnat National Category:Algerian Ligue Professionnelle 1 seasons Category:1973–74 in Algerian football Algeria
